member.summary:
            Access Token Service is used to get long access token / access token.

To get access token following fields will be require: Request Token (oauth_token) and Verifier (oauth_verifier) from the merchant callback.
For Pairing during checkout, this service will need to be called twice.


To exchange for a Long Access Token which is used to retrieve precheckout data.

To exchange for an Access Token which is used to retrieve checkout data.


